'''《毒堇之杯》'''（''The Hemlock Cup: Socrates, Athens, and the Search for the Good Life''）是英国历史学家[[贝塔妮·休斯|贝塔妮·休斯]]的一部关于古希腊哲学家[[苏格拉底|苏格拉底]]的通俗历史著作，2011年由[[Vintage_Books|Vintage Books]]出版<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.penguinrandomhouse.com/books/83947/the-hemlock-cup-by-bettany-hughes/9781400076017 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-07-23 |archive-date=2019-07-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190707161114/https://www.penguinrandomhouse.com/books/83947/the-hemlock-cup-by-bettany-hughes/9781400076017 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

《毒堇之杯》一书被列入[[纽约时报畅销书榜|纽约时报畅销书榜]]，并被《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》选为年度图书<ref>{{cite news|date=19 November 2010|title=Books of the Year for Christmas: History|newspaper=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]]|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/topics/christmas/8142784/Books-of-the-Year-for-Christmas-History.html|accessdate=11 April 2012|archive-date=2020-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200724013134/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/topics/christmas/8142784/Books-of-the-Year-for-Christmas-History.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，被[[BBC廣播四台|BBC廣播四台]]作为本周图书推荐<ref>{{cite web|title=Book of the Week: The Hemlock Cup: Socrates, Athens and the Search for the Good Life|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00wh306|accessdate=11 April 2012|work=Book of the Week|publisher=BBC Radio 4|archive-date=2020-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200723093520/https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00wh306|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并入围作家协会奖<ref>{{cite web|title=Writer's Guild Awards 2011|url=http://www.writersguild.org.uk/news-a-features/general/225-writers-guild-awards-2011-winners|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120414233051/http://www.writersguild.org.uk/news-a-features/general/225-writers-guild-awards-2011-winners|archivedate=14 April 2012|accessdate=14 October 2013|work=writersguild.org.uk}}</ref>。

